      <div class="fq-a">Adults pay €10.50 (120 NOK). Children under 18 enter free. Senior citizens 67+, people with disabilities, students, and military conscripts pay €8.50 (100 NOK). UiT university students enter free with a valid student card. Prices listed are 2025 rates — check en.uit.no/tmu/polarmuseet/planlegg for current figures.</div>
